# One line-ending policy for all machines. Repo stores LF; the working tree is LF
# everywhere (Windows VS and the Linux VM share these files on disk, so they must
# agree). eol=lf overrides each machine's core.autocrlf.
* text=auto eol=lf

*.png binary

# Vendored third-party JS libraries (committed in-tree because the hosted-WASM stack
# has no bundler/CDN to resolve them at build or runtime). Exclude from language stats,
# collapse in diffs/PRs, and don't try to merge them — treat as opaque blobs.
src/PgmStudio.Client/wwwroot/js/studio/vendor/** linguist-vendored linguist-generated -diff -merge
